data.description: Come see this charming cape cod home in the heart of Christiansburg. You will enjoy main level living with the primary suite, a second bedroom, laundry, and living area on the first floor. The home has a brand new roof and cosmetic updates throughout. Walking distance from the Christiansburg Rec Center and Huckleberry trail, and minutes away from restaurants, shopping and I-81 access, the convenience of this location is hard to beat! Come see it today - it won't last long!
